	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you're ever interested in reverse-engineering a commercial sound engine for CPU-saving tricks, Isolated Warrior (and probably most other games developed by KID) might be worth your time. It has some pretty "complicated" music, yet uses less CPU than some other relatively simple engines (i.e. Mega Man 2).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


