	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I wonder exactly how Famitracker's sound engine stands up to the rest CPU-usage wise.  But yeah, Capcom's sound engine is notoriously inefficient.  I've heard about it from romhacking message boards.  People have optimized the sound engine to get more CPU time for their megaman romhacks.

		

